Recursion Relation : 

T(n) = {
          O(1)  if n==1
          T(n/2)+c  if n>1  
        }
  
Time Complexity(with recr & without recr) : 
Worst case & average case = O( log(n) )
best case  =  O(1)

Space Complexity(with recr) : nB [array size] + log(n)B [stack space]
                            = O( n )
                            
Space Complexity(without recr) : nB [array size] + cB [variable size]
                            = O( n )
